<br>
My typical DPS when tanking in upper rats in CoD is around 70(lvl 62, ambidex aa). But even with BoC I am having trouble keeping mobs off the 16 dam piercer rogues I group with, at least the first 10-20 seconds of fight, until I get an EB proc and/or they get a few evades in.<br>
<br>
Anyway, I have enough DKP saved up to be able to buy either BBB, Emp 2HS or Emp 1HS when they drop for us.<br>
<br>
From what I hear Bloodied Bezerker's Blade(BBB) is one of the better DPS/agro choices. And is the one I am primarily looking into getting.<br>
<br>
Will BBB outdamage BoC+Primal? And is it better agro than BoC+primal? If BBB does not represent a substantial DPS upgrade over BoC+Primal, there is no point in me buying one.<br>
<br>
(And if I were to use BBB fulltime I would not be swapping in primal, as I hate hotswapping weapons, and I dont have a primal 2Hander.)<br>
<br>
I am guessing the emp 2H is decent DPS too, but I am afraid it will not generate enough agro to tank without trouble(read: mashing taunt button like a maniac) in normal exp groups?<br>
<br>
And where would an Acrylia Handled Broadsword+Primal combo end up in the scheme of things? This would probably be my second choice after BBB, I am thinking it would be a nice DPS boost from my current combo, but I might lose some taunt value from the EB procs. Not sure how severe the loss of EB proc would feel like. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rani>rani</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalWhite.gif" BORDER=0> at: 11/12/02 12:08:50 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=grimmlokk>Grimmlokk</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/icon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 970<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/12/02 12:23:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4389.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/spinhead2.gif?flezbwidth=30&flezbheight=41? WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Emp 2h,BBB or Emp1Hs+Primal for DPS+agro in exp groups?</span><hr size=1>  Purely anecdotal evidence, but friend war with BBB has zero trouble pulling agro off me using BoC/Primal. In fact has trouble keeping agro off himself fairly often. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6122"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/bustedteef2.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=matthiaskathandrion>Matthias Kathandrion</A></span><br> <s